    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund Memorial for Gaza Children Honouring Peace, Compassion",
        "additional_details": "We think this memorial would honour Gaza\u2019s children, a solemn reminder of the devastating human cost of conflict. We think it would reinforce the UK\u2019s dedication to peace and humanity, fostering reflection, healing, and solidarity. We think it would educate future generations on the importance of protecting the innocent in war, strengthening the UK\u2019s moral leadership and commitment to compassion.",
        "background": "We ask the Government to fund a memorial to honour Gaza\u2019s children lost to conflict. We think this memorial would promote peace, compassion, and reflection, complementing existing monuments that uphold justice, humanity, and equality.",
